OL,5,GOfcom is expected to say soon whether
OL,6,Git will run a full consultation on
OL,7,Gchanges to the TV advertising rules.
OL,9,FIt sought views over the summer on
OL,10,Fwhether there was a case to change the
OL,11,Fextra rules covering ITV, Channel 4 and
OL,12,FChannel 5.
OL,14,FThe three PSBs have less advertising in
OL,15,Ftotal than other commercial channels
OL,16,Fand rules on the frequency of breaks
OL,17,Fare tighter.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
