OL,5,FBut if you've been watching I'm a
OL,6,FCelebrity, you'll be aware of the kind
OL,7,Fof archaic compromises ITV has to make
OL,8,Fto stay within the rules.
OL,10,FITV is allowed 40 minutes of
OL,11,Fadvertising between 6pm and 11pm with
OL,12,Fno more than 12 minutes in each hour.
OL,14,FOn a typical weeknight, there are 4
OL,15,Fminutes of ads before 7pm with the
OL,16,Fremaining 36 minutes shared out between
OL,17,F7pm and the start of News at Ten.
OL,19,FHowever the channel naturally wants to
OL,20,Fmake the best use of the limited
OL,21,Fadvertising time available.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
OL,22,                                   G2/6
