OL,5,FI'm a Celebrity runs until around
OL,6,F10.30pm some evenings. So advertising
OL,7,Fis taken away from less lucrative slots
OL,8,Fso it can be slotted into the ratings
OL,9,Fjuggernaut.
OL,11,FFor instance, on Monday and Tuesday
OL,12,Flast week, there were no ad breaks
OL,13,Fbetween the start of the regional news
OL,14,Fat 6pm and Emmerdale at 7.30pm.
OL,16,FBut if you imagine there was some
OL,17,Fbenefit to viewers in this, think
OL,18,Fagain.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
