OL,5,FInstead, the network news followed its
OL,6,Fusual format but the ad breaks were
OL,7,Freplaced by what I call the Trailer
OL,8,FBreaks of Doom.
OL,10,FThese are the full-length breaks
OL,11,Fdesigned for commercials which are
OL,12,Ffilled entirely by promotions because
OL,13,Fof the rules on the volume of
OL,14,Fadvertising on PSBs.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
