OL,5,FIt is important to look properly at
OL,6,Fwhether there are genuine economic
OL,7,Fbenefits to advertisers and
OL,8,Fbroadcasters from allowing more
OL,9,Fadvertising. It is possible they may
OL,10,Fconclude that the same amount of
OL,11,Fadvertising spending could simply be
OL,12,Fspread more thinly.
OL,14,FIt should also be clear that
OL,15,Fbroadcasters do not need to use their
OL,16,Fwhole allocation if they conclude that
OL,17,F"less is more"  could rationed
OL,18,Fadvertising command a premium or boost
OL,19,Fratings?
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
