OL,5,FBut, as I've argued before, it is hard
OL,6,Fto claim that viewers will lose out if
OL,7,FITV and others have a full 12 minutes
OL,8,Fof ads all through the most popular
OL,9,Fviewing hours.
OL,11,FPromo breaks are, if anything, more
OL,12,Ffrustrating for viewers but do not pay
OL,13,Ffor the content.
